                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="font-weight-700">Fuel Capacity:</span> 14L – 17L
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="font-weight-700">Seat Height:</span> 770mm – 810mm
                    </li>
                </ol>
                <div class="row m-b20">
                    <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 text-center">
                        <img src="~/images/latestnews/2024/nov/brixtonmotorcyclestodebutinindiaonnovember18keydetailsrevealed/1.webp" alt="Brixton Motorcycles India Launch 2" />
